OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 8 Mar to Tue 17 MarFA
OL,6,Fbroad northwest-southeast split in the
OL,7,Fweather looks the most likely scenario
OL,8,Fas we move into the second week of
OL,9,FMarch. High pressure centred over
OL,10,Fcontinental Europe should maintain
OL,11,Fenough of an influence across southern
OL,12,Fand eastern UK to allow for a fair bit
OL,13,Fof dry and at times bright weather,
OL,14,Fwhilst the majority of rain-bearing
OL,15,Fweather systems affect the northwest
OL,16,Fof the UK. Some strong winds are
OL,17,Flikely at times in the northwest.
OL,18,FTemperatures look to be mostly near to
OL,19,Fa little above average. Towards the
OL,20,Fend of this period, there is chance
OL,21,Fthat unsettled conditions in the
OL,22,Fnorthwest may become rather more
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fwidespread.
